            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3606Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of three episodes/events, showing: first, the custodian of the church standing in front of the sitting Kaṭir ordering him to leave the church;
                    second, <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> sitting on a throne surrounded by two <term key="angel">angels</term> with the custodian of the church 
                    sitting before her; third, Kaṭir standing before <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>, who is sitting on throne and performs a <term key="gestureblessing">blessing gesture</term>.</p>
                <p>Images available at <ref target="https://pemm.princeton.edu/en-us/paintings/by-story/82">https://pemm.princeton.edu/en-us/paintings/by-story/82</ref></p>
